data.description: Welcome to your perfect oasis—a single-family home on a generous half-acre lot, boasting not only a spacious and comfortable interior but also awe-inspiring mountain views visible from the living room and dining room. Enjoy the serenity and beauty of nature right from the heart of your home.    Step outside onto the deck at the back—a perfect extension of your living space—where you can soak in the panoramic mountain views. Whether it's a quiet morning coffee or lively evening gatherings, this outdoor haven is destined to be a favorite spot.    The backyard is more than just a yard; it's your private escape. Imagine evenings gathered around the fire pit, creating memories under the starlit sky. With the entire property fenced in, you'll experience both privacy and security.    Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this residence features five bedrooms and three bathrooms, offering the ideal combination of comfort and convenience. The well-designed layout and picturesque surroundings make this home a haven for both relaxation and entertainment.    Seize the opportunity to make this property, with its perfect blend of nature and modern living, your very own retreat. Don't miss out on the chance to experience the tranquility and beauty that this home offers!
